snippet.title: "Amber Is Lying" Lily-Rose Depp Speaks on How Innocent Johnny Depp Is (IG Live)
snippet.description:
"Amber Is Lying" Lily-Rose Depp Speaks on How Innocent Johnny Depp Is (IG Live)
“Amber is lying.” Lily-Rose Depp, the 21-year old daughter of Johnny Depp and his former partner Vanessa Paradis, has spoken up. Lily’s statements against Amber Heard are making rounds on social media, and Johnny Depp fans are overjoyed over the fact that Lily-Rose left no stone unturned in defending her father, Johnny Depp. In style reports that “Lily-Rose Depp Takes To Instagram To Defend Her Father Johnny Depp.” So, what did Lily-Rose say to back her father, Johnny Depp against Amber Heard? Let’s find out in this video.  

Here on Film Streak we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assure that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning you favorite actors!
